# OS
.DS_Store

# Project notes — only README, REFERENCES, RELEASE_NOTES are tracked at the
# repo root.  Audit ledgers, design docs, plans, ideas, and module-health
# trackers stay local.  Sub-directory .md files (e.g. python/README.md,
# documents/README.md) are unaffected by the /*.md anchor.
/*.md
!/README.md
!/REFERENCES.md
!/RELEASE_NOTES.md
